<s-1 id="RM000001IQJ001X_01_0030" proc-id="RM0250U___00001G600000">
<ptxt>INSTALL NO. 1 OIL PIPE
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Make sure that there is no foreign matter on the mesh of the oil control valve filter LH.</ptxt>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Do not touch the mesh when installing the oil control valve filter.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the oil control valve filter LH to the oil pipe union. Install new gaskets and temporarily install the oil pipe (on the head cover side).</ptxt>
