<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>65</t-value1>
<t-value2>663</t-value2>
<t-value4>48</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<atten3>
<ptxt>If the link that connects the gaskets is broken, remove the connecting link by using nippers or similar tools.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
